  "intent_precise": "111210-part-9.ot2.apiv2: Using tc_plate (pcr_plate, slot 4), temp_plate (labware, slot 6), pcr_tubes (labware, slot 2). With thermocycler module, temperature module. (1) Pause: Please replace the empty tip racks! (2) Set temperature to 4\u00b0C. (3) Pause: Temperature Module has been cooled to 4\u00b0C.\n              Please place your samples and reagents on the\n              temperature module. (4) Transfer 7\u00b5L from source to destination. (5) Mix 7 times at 10\u00b5L. (6) Transfer 20\u00b5L from source to destination. (7) Operate thermocycler. (8) Set temperature to 95\u00b0C. (9) Run thermocycler profile for 21 cycles. (10) Set temperature to 72\u00b0C. (11) Set temperature to 4\u00b0C. (12) Set temperature to 4\u00b0C. (13) Open thermocycler lid.",
